1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:03,450
This is the same deal through different ledger views.

2
00:00:03,450 --> 00:00:07,630
Each Funder sees only contracts it is entitled to see.

3
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:10,989
The Coordinator sees no quote contents.

4
00:00:10,989 --> 00:00:17,122
The Auditor sees nothing before settlement, and the Outsider sees nothing useful.

5
00:00:17,122 --> 00:00:21,848
This privacy comes from Canton disclosure, not a visual filter.

